RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT cc.contract_ref_no, cc.user_ref_no, cc.counterparty, sc.customer_name1, cc.contract_ccy, lsm.amount FROM oltbs_contract cc, lbtbs_syndication_master lsm, sttm_core_customer sc WHERE cc.contract_ref_no = lsm.contract_ref_no AND cc.latest_version_no = lsm.version_no AND sc.customer_no = cc.counterparty AND cc.module_code = 'FC' AND cc.auth_status = 'A' AND sc.RECORD_STAT='O' AND sc.AUTH_STAT='A' AND cc.contract_status = 'A' AND cc.branch = NVL(?,global.current_branch) AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM olvw_avl_prod_br_usr c, olvw_user_products s WHERE s.user_id = c.user_id AND s.product_code = c.product_code AND cc.product_code = c.product_code AND cc.branch = c.branch_code AND s.user_id = GLOBAL.user_id)

select a.BORROWER_TRANCHE_PRODUCT, b.Product_description from lbtms_facility_tr_product a, oltms_product b, oltms_product_master_ld c, olvw_avl_prod_br_usr d where a.product_code = sypks_utils.get_product(?) AND A.BORROWER_TRANCHE_PRODUCT = b.product_code AND B.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND B.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND c.product = b.product_code AND b.product_code = d.product_code AND d.branch_code = NVL(?,global.current_branch) AND d.user_id = global.user_id AND c.PARTICIPANT_PRODUCT IS NOT NULL AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT K, OLVW_USER_PRODUCTS S WHERE S.USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID AND S.PRODUCT_CODE = K.PRODUCT_CODE AND S.PRODUCT_CODE = B.PRODUCT_CODE)

SELECT a.customer_no, b.short_name, b.customer_name1 FROM lbtbs_contract_borrowers a, oltms_customer b WHERE a.contract_ref_no = ? AND a.customer_no = b.customer_no AND b.auth_stat = 'A' AND b.record_stat = 'O' AND a.version_no = (SELECT MAX(version_no) FROM lbtbs_contract_borrowers c where c.contract_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no) and exists (select 1 from olvws_product_customers o where o.product_code = ? and o.customer_no = b.customer_no)
select a.ccy_code, a.ccy_name from cytms_ccy_defn a, olvws_product_currencies v where a.ccy_code = v.ccy_code and a.record_Stat = 'O' and a.auth_stat = 'A' and v.product_code = ?
SELECT BRANCH_CODE, BRANCH_NAME FROM OLTMS_BRANCH WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'

SELECT AC_GL_NO, AC_GL_CCY, AC_GL_DESC FROM OLTBS_ACCOUNT A WHERE (BRANCH_CODE IS NOT NULL OR AC_OR_GL = 'G') AND GL_ACLASS_TYPE <> TO_CHAR(5) AND AC_GL_REC_STATUS = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND NVL(BRANCH_CODE, ?) = ? AND (A.AC_OR_GL = 'G' OR (A.AC_OR_GL = 'A' AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM OLVWS_PROD_ACNT_ACCESS X WHERE X.AC_GL_NO = A.AC_GL_NO AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = ?))) ORDER BY DECODE(NVL(AC_GL_CCY, '*'), ?, 1, 2), DECODE(NVL(CUST_NO, '*'), ?, 1, 2), AC_GL_NO, BRANCH_CODE

SELECT AC_GL_NO, AC_GL_CCY, AC_GL_DESC FROM OLTBS_ACCOUNT A WHERE (BRANCH_CODE IS NOT NULL OR AC_OR_GL = 'G') AND GL_ACLASS_TYPE <> TO_CHAR(5) AND AC_GL_REC_STATUS = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND (A.AC_OR_GL = 'G' OR (A.AC_OR_GL = 'A' AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM OLVWS_PROD_ACNT_ACCESS X WHERE X.AC_GL_NO = A.AC_GL_NO AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = ?))) ORDER BY DECODE(NVL(AC_GL_CCY, '*'), ?, 1, 2), DECODE(NVL(CUST_NO, '*'), ?, 1, 2), AC_GL_NO, BRANCH_CODE
SELECT ADMIN_ID, ADMIN_NAME FROM OLTMS_ADMINISTRATOR WHERE AUTH_STAT = 'A'
SELECT INDUSTRY_CODE FROM OLTMS_INDUSTRY WHERE AUTH_STAT='A' AND RECORD_STAT='O'

SELECT A.CCY, B.CCY_NAME FROM LBTBS_BORROWER_CCY A,CYTMS_CCY_DEFN B, OLTBS_CONTRACT C WHERE A.CCY = B.CCY_CODE AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = C.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND A.VERSION_NO = C.LATEST_VERSION_NO AND NVL(A.BLOCK_CCY,'N') <>'Y' ORDER BY A.CCY

SELECT SSI_MNEMONIC, SETTLEMENT_SEQ_NO, BRANCH, PAY_ACCOUNT, RECV_ACCOUNT, COUNTERPARTY, CURRENCY, PRODUCT_CODE, MODULE FROM OLTM_INSTR WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM olvws_PROD_ACNT_Access X WHERE (PAY_ACCOUNT = X.AC_GL_NO or RECV_ACCOUNT = X.AC_GL_NO) AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = ?)

SELECT SSI_MNEMONIC, SETTLEMENT_SEQ_NO, BRANCH, PAY_ACCOUNT, RECV_ACCOUNT, COUNTERPARTY, CURRENCY, PRODUCT_CODE, MODULE FROM OLTM_INSTR WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM olvws_PROD_ACNT_Access X WHERE (PAY_ACCOUNT = X.AC_GL_NO or RECV_ACCOUNT = X.AC_GL_NO) AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = ?)

SELECT AC_GL_NO, AC_GL_CCY, AC_GL_DESC FROM OLTBS_ACCOUNT A WHERE (BRANCH_CODE IS NOT NULL OR AC_OR_GL = 'G') AND GL_ACLASS_TYPE <> TO_CHAR(5) AND AC_GL_REC_STATUS = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM OLVWS_PROD_ACNT_ACCESS X WHERE X.AC_GL_NO = A.AC_GL_NO AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = ?) ORDER BY DECODE(NVL(AC_GL_CCY, '*'), ?, 1, 2), DECODE(NVL(CUST_NO, '*'), ?, 1, 2), AC_GL_NO, BRANCH_CODE

SELECT A.CUSTOMER_NO , B.SHORT_NAME FROM OLVWS_PRODUCT_CUSTOMERS A, OLTMS_CUSTOMER B WHERE A.PRODUCT_CODE = ? AND A.CUSTOMER_NO = B.CUSTOMER_NO AND B.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND B.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLTMS_BRANCH_PARAMETERS C WHERE C.BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND C.ROUNDING_PARTICIPANT = B.CUSTOMER_NO) ORDER BY CUSTOMER_NO

SELECT COMPONENT FROM (SELECT COMPONENT FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_DFLT_SCHEDULES A WHERE PRODUCT = ? AND A.SCHEDULE_TYPE = DECODE(?, 'C', 'P', 'X') UNION Select COMPONENT From lftms_product_fee Where product_code = ? And nvl(stop_association, 'N') = 'N') WHERE COMPONENT NOT IN (SELECT COMPONENT FROM LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE MAS WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND COMPONENT_STATUS = 'V' AND EVENT_SEQ_NO = (SELECT MAX(EVENT_SEQ_NO) FROM LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE DET WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND MAS.COMPONENT=DET.COMPONENT))

RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_MULTIBRN_WHERECLAUSE: MODULE_CODE='LB' AND PRODUCT_TYPE='C' AND Branch IN (SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVW_USER_BRANCHES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID INTERSECT SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMTB_USER_ROLE WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID UNION SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVWS_USER_CENTRAL_ROLES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID)

RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTBS_ACC_COLL_LINK_DTL.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER.BRANCH = LBTBS_ACC_COLL_LINK_DTL.BRANCH_CODE AND OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER.VERSION_NO = LBTBS_ACC_COLL_LINK_DTL.VERSION_NO

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT * FROM ((SELECT 'A' Default_Liab, l.Line_Code || l.Line_Serial Linkage_Ref_No, 'F' Linkage_Type, (SELECT Liab_No FROM Sttm_Core_El_Liab WHERE Id = l.Liab_Id) Liab_No, Cust.Customer_No Customer_No, l.Brn Branch, l.Line_Currency Currency, l.Description, l.Line_Expiry_Date Expiry_Date, l.facility_type facility_type FROM Sttm_Core_El_Facility l, Sttm_Core_El_Liab_Cust Cust WHERE l.Record_Stat = 'O' AND Cust.Record_Stat = 'O' AND Cust.Auth_Stat = 'A' AND l.Liab_Id = Cust.Liab_Id AND l.Once_Auth = 'Y' AND l.Availability_Flag = 'Y' AND Nvl('CCY', ?) = 'CCY' AND Nvl('LIABCIF', ?) = 'LIABCIF' AND Nvl('CNPTY', ?) = 'CNPTY' AND Nvl('PRDCD', ?) = 'PRDCD' AND Nvl('BRN', ?) = 'BRN' AND Nvl('CCY', ?) = 'CCY') UNION (SELECT 'A' Default_Liab, Pp.Pool_Code Linkage_Ref_No, 'P' Linkage_Type, (SELECT Liab_No FROM Sttm_Core_El_Liab WHERE Id = Pp.Liab_Id) Liab_No, Cust.Customer_No Customer_No, Pp.Branch_Code Branch, Pool_Ccy Currency, Pp.Pool_Description, NULL Expiry_Date, NULL facility_type FROM Sttm_Core_El_Pool Pp, Sttm_Core_El_Liab_Cust Cust WHERE Pp.Record_Stat = 'O' AND Cust.Record_Stat = 'O' AND Cust.Auth_Stat = 'A' AND Cust.Liab_Id = Pp.Liab_Id AND Pp.Once_Auth = 'Y') UNION (SELECT 'A' Default_Liab, c.Collateral_Code Linkage_Ref_No, 'T' Linkage_Type, (SELECT Liab_No FROM Sttm_Core_El_Liab WHERE Id = c.Liab_Id) Liab_No, Cust.Customer_No Customer_No, c.Branch_Code Branch, c.Collateral_Currency Currency, c.Collateral_Description, c.End_Date Expiry_Date, NULL facility_type FROM Sttm_Core_El_Collat c, Sttm_Core_El_Liab_Cust Cust WHERE Cust.Liab_Id = c.Liab_Id AND c.Available = 'Y' AND c.Record_Stat = 'O' AND Cust.Record_Stat = 'O' AND Cust.Auth_Stat = 'A' AND c.Once_Auth = 'Y') UNION (SELECT 'A' Default_Liab, c.Liab_No Linkage_Ref_No, 'L' Linkage_Type, c.Liab_No, Cust.Customer_No Customer_No, c.Liab_Branch Branch, c.Liab_Ccy Currency, c.Liab_Name, NULL AS Expiry_Date, NULL facility_type FROM Sttm_Core_El_Liab c, Sttm_Core_El_Liab_Cust Cust WHERE Cust.Liab_Id = c.Id AND c.Record_Stat = 'O' AND Cust.Record_Stat = 'O' AND Cust.Auth_Stat = 'A' AND c.Once_Auth = 'Y')) WHERE Customer_No = Nvl(?, ?) AND Linkage_Type = ? AND (('A' = ?) OR ('S' = ? AND Liab_No = ?) OR Default_Liab = ?)
SELECT A.CUSTOMER_NO,A.CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM OLTMS_CUSTOMER A WHERE AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' ORDER BY A.CUSTOMER_NO

SELECT x.CUSTOMER_NO CUSTOMER_NO,b.CUSTOMER_NAME1 CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM lbtbs_Contract_Borrowers x,OLTMS_CUSTOMER b where contract_ref_no = ? AND x.CUSTOMER_NO = b.CUSTOMER_NO AND b.record_stat = 'O' AND version_no = (SELECT max(version_no) FROM lbtbs_syndication_master WHERE contract_ref_no = ?)UNION SELECT A.CUSTOMER_NO CUSTOMER_NO,A.CUSTOMER_NAME1 CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM OLTMS_CUSTOMER A WHERE A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' and once_auth='Y'and A.CUSTOMER_NO NOT IN(SELECT PORTFOLIO FROM TLTMS_PORTFOLIO b WHERE b.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND b.RECORD_STAT = 'O')
SELECT FIN_CENTRE,FIN_CENTRE_DESC FROM OLTM_FIN_CENTRE WHERE RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A'
